data.description: Enjoy country living in this well designed home on over one and third acres (1.39).  3 bedrooms. 2 baths.shower in Master tub/shower in guest bath. New laminate flooring. New counter tops in the Kitchen and bath. Laundry room. Dining area. Large living room. Covered back porch. TWO full 60 AMP RV hookups (water, electric and sewer). 2 large out buildings for storage or work shop. Nearby shopping and health care in towns of Willcox, AZ and Benson, AZ. Beautiful mountain views. Mild climate. Fresh air!
